text: Victoria Spartz (n√©e Kulheyko) (); born October 6, 1978) is a Ukrainian- American politician and businesswoman. She is a member of the United States House of Representatives from Indiana's 5th congressional district since 2021. Spartz is the first Ukrainian-born member of the U.S. Congress and the first member born in a then-Soviet Republic. She was a member of the Indiana Senate from the 20th District. In February 2023, Spartz announced that she would not run for reelection or any other office in 2024. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Naturalized citizens of the United States Category:United States representatives from Indiana Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Members of the Indiana General Assembly
